column5: Went down to Dunnville to try to get us some of them big cats, was a slow but beautiful day not many people from shore catching, we managed a couple towards the evening.   here's the vid.
Wow, goood job guys. Those were some great looking catfish alright....love the golden colour to them.   Thanks for sharing!
Great report and video al  Looks like you guys had fun hooking into those big cats.... Congratulations  Thanks for sharing Leechman
